Adds a menu to show weapons

[h2]Location[/h2]
Main Menu > Options > Weapons

[h2]Bugs[/h2]
If you have an issue with the mod please write in the steam discussion:
[url]https://steamcommunity.com/workshop/filedetails/discussion/2974580070/6374326702129204875/[/url]
or open up an issue on github:
[url]https://github.com/otDan/Brotato-WeaponExplorer/issues[/url]



posting a review with something like "it's not working", "it crashes my game", 
"I don't see the menu" will be ignored and the comment will be deleted